<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Sparks Beta</title>

  <!-- build:css bower_components/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.js -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bower_components/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css">
  <!-- endbuild-->

  <!-- build:js bower_components/lodash/lodash.min.js -->
  <script src="/bower_components/lodash/lodash.js"></script>
  <!-- endbuild -->

  <!-- build:js bower_components/chance/chance.min.js -->
  <script src="/bower_components/chance/chance.js"></script>
  <!-- endbuild -->

  <!-- build:js bower_components/webcomponentsjs/webcomponents-lite.min.js -->
  <script src="/bower_components/webcomponentsjs/webcomponents-lite.js"></script>
  <!-- endbuild -->

  <!-- will be replaced with elements/elements.vulcanized.html -->
  <link rel="import" href="/elements/elements.html">
  <!-- endreplace-->

  <!-- build:css styles/main.css -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
  <!-- endbuild-->

  <!-- For shared styles, shared-styles.html import in elements.html -->
  <style is="custom-style" include="index-styles">
    paper-input.huge {
      --paper-input-container-input: {
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 36px;
      };
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body unresolved class="fullbleed layout vertical index">
  <template is="dom-bind" id="app">
    <!-- Main Area -->
    <paper-scroll-header-panel main condenses keep-condensed-header>

      <!-- Main Toolbar -->
      <paper-toolbar id="mainToolbar" class="tall">
        <span class="flex"></span>

        <!-- Toolbar links -->
        <nav>
          <a href="https://github.com/northernlight/sparks">
            <i class="fa fa-github fa-2x"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="/#about">
            <i class="fa fa-question-circle fa-2x"></i>
          </a>
        </nav>

        <!-- Application name -->
        <div class="middle middle-container center horizontal layout">
            <div class="app-name">
              <i class="fa fa-cogs fa-inverse"></i> Sparks <span class="small">beta</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Application sub title -->
        <div class="bottom bottom-container center horizontal layout">
          <div class="bottom-title paper-font-subhead">Sparks is hip. Sparks is cool.</div>
        </div>

      </paper-toolbar>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div id="content">
        <section id="intro">
          <div class="container">
            <form is="iron-form" id="sessionForm" method="get" action="/session">
              <paper-input class="huge" label="Create or join a session" char-counter auto-validate pattern="[a-zA-Z0-9]*" maxlength="20" error-message="letters and numbers only!" size="20" value="{{sessionID}}" autofocus>
              </paper-input>
            </form>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section id="about" class="content">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="user-story">
              <i class="fa fa-inverse fa-video-camera fa-4x fa-pull-left fa-border"></i>
            Using the latest web technogies like WebRTC or the Polymer framework Sparks provides a simple, lightweight web conferencing tool, which requires no registration nor further software but the preinstalled browser.
            Use Sparks for private purposes such as chatting with partners all over the world. Stay in touch with Sparks.
            Providing a powerful end-to-end encryption qualifies Sparks also for sharing sensitive data or as a replacement for your current business conferencing software.
            Stay connected with your business partners using Sparks.
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </paper-scroll-header-panel>
  </template>

  <!-- build:js scripts/layout.min.js -->
  <script src="/js/layout.js"></script>
  <!-- endbuild-->

  <script>
    app.sessionID = chance.word({syllables: 5});
  </script>
</body>
